{"tid":2175873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"由陳彥霖一案見到政府準備將示威者描述成受毒品/金錢引誘","createTime":"2020-08-26T17:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T06:34:22.000Z","uid":6058,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"60923e444a2ca3b493357d16b191c55dbd9f6f12","tid":2175873,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T17:30:11.000Z","msg":"佢哋一時話佢好似精神病<br />\n一時話目光呆滯<br />\n好明顯想將自己嘅錯spin去毒品/金錢引誘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJrKWxc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJrKWxc.png&h=cdecff70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後想叫人唔好再信示威者/黃絲<br />\n而呢個說法將會同721嘅黑白顛倒一樣<br />\n佢哋會不斷講不斷講<br />\n之後就當係史實<br />\n就好似8964咁話冇死過人"},{"pid":"55ae4e77e8615609f5e4d1bf0538a767a01e82cc","tid":2175873,"uid":201237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T17:35:28.000Z","msg":"推, 對家又想抹黑過身嘅手足"},{"pid":"ed5ce263143f9ce6bc7da57313d149f2e9c2d291","tid":2175873,"uid":301152,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:02:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"violet\"><span class=\"xx-large\">3個專科醫生</span><br />\n都認為彥霖<span class=\"x-large\">冇思覺失調</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">青山醫院兒童及青少年精神科醫生楊禹行</span>指，陳彥霖在8月19日因將頭撞向牆及咬傷前臂等原因入院，判斷她為急性壓力反應及對立反叛症，但交談時認為她說話清晰，沒有思覺失調的症狀，包括無幻聽、幻覺等，不過其母親拒絕為她安排精神科覆診，又解釋雖然她聲稱腦海聽到聲音，並非好像如思覺失調病人般，認為聲音真實存在的來自外界，所以判斷她沒有幻聽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"> 另一位精神科醫生鍾加詠</span>供稱，她於 8 月 21 日為陳彥霖會診。她當日<span class=\"red\">亦診斷陳彥霖為對立反抗症</span>，為她處方鎮靜藥物，供有需要時使用，但最終醫院急症室有無為她注射鎮靜劑，鍾則表示她並不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而<span class=\"orange\">青山醫院女精神科醫生歐陽穎賢</span>今供稱，去年3月13日她於屯門醫院急症室病房與彥霖會診。彥霖當時態度冷靜平和，說話有條理、情緒穩定，沒提及有自殺或暴力行為，並否認有幻覺、幻聽或妄想症狀。歐陽指彥霖責怪社工不信守承諾，並延長她在寄宿學校的住宿時間。<span class=\"orange\">歐陽診斷彥霖患有急性壓力症，以及對立反抗症。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%99%B3%E5%BD%A5%E9%9C%96%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%A0%E7%A0%94%E8%A8%8A-%E9%99%B3%E6%AF%8D%E5%92%8C%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%91%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%B0%B1%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E6%9C%89%E5%90%A6%E8%81%BD%E5%88%B0%E7%94%B7%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%B2-%E8%AA%AA%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%8C%87%E7%84%A1%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25BD%25A5%25E9%259C%2596%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25A0%2594%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%2592%258C%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25A7%2591%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%2581%25BD%25E5%2588%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2581%25B2-%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2587%25B4-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%2F&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatkn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=559857ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25BD%25A5%25E9%259C%2596%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25A0%2594%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%2592%258C%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25A7%2591%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%2581%25BD%25E5%2588%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2581%25B2-%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2587%25B4-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%2F&h=602c354a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%99%B3%E5%BD%A5%E9%9C%96%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%A0%E7%A0%94%E8%A8%8A-%E9%99%B3%E6%AF%8D%E5%92%8C%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%91%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%B0%B1%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E6%9C%89%E5%90%A6%E8%81%BD%E5%88%B0%E7%94%B7%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%B2-%E8%AA%AA%E6%